2 × Drone Brushless Motors (~10k RPM)	Propulsion
2 × ESC (Electronic Speed Controllers)	Motor control
Servo Motor	Rudder steering
Bicycle Spokes	Propeller shafts
Custom Metal Propellers	Water propulsion
Thermocol Hull	Boat structure
LiPo Battery	Power source


